Resource Profile: fiphr-sd-bloodpressure

Official URL: http://phr.kanta.fi/StructureDefinition/fiphr-sd-bloodpressure Version: 0.3.0
Draft as of 2021-02-22 Computable Name: FIPHRSDBloodpressure

Finnish PHR profile for blood pressure measurement

Finnish PHR profile for Observation used in blood pressure measurements.The profile is based on the Finnish PHR observation profile.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Observation/bloodpressure-max, Observation/bloodpressure-min
